10.2: What is JSON? Part I

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_NFkzw6oFtQ&list=PLRqwX-V7Uu6a-SQiI4RtIwuOrLJGnel0r&index=2

To add json data to a js file:

loadJSON();

Also:

loadImage();
loadTable();

etc.

10.4: Loading JSON data from a URL (Asynchronous Callbacks!)

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6mT3r8Qn1VY&list=PLRqwX-V7Uu6a-SQiI4RtIwuOrLJGnel0r&index=4

Asynchronous Callbacks

loadJSON(_,_)

--> first argument is the URL for the data
--> second argument is a callback function

-add parameter to call callback function definition
--> gotData(_) --> parameter is in parenthesis, p5.js will fill function with data

